{"id":"6034","name":"happy-hour-tough-as-nails","title":"Happy Hour: Tough As Nails","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2010-11-12T17:30:00-06:00","tags":["christmas tree","david kernall","dickson county","extreme makeover","fema","flood relief","hacking","lighthouse christian school","military appreciation day","nashville zoo","sarah palin","veterans day"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/denisemattox/5169966491/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1228/5169966491_0b7e3593d1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"375\" height=\"500\"></a></div><ul><li>Don&#x2019;t forget to set those DVRs! The Extreme Makeover episode featuring Nashville&#x2019;s Lighthouse Christian School getting a post-flood makeover will air this Sunday at 7pm. Tune in an hour earlier to see some behind-the-scenes stuff courtesy of News Channel 2. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=13490934\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>Metro is searching for the perfect Christmas tree this year. They&#x2019;re looking for a 30-40&#x2032; Norway or Blue Spruce that will <a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/12/09/happy-hour-yes-were-still-giggling-about-the-tree/\" target=\"_blank\">preferably remain vertical</a> for the duration of the holiday season. Email <a href=\"mailto:Randall.Lantz@nashville.gov\" target=\"_blank\">Randall Lantz</a> if you have any information. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/community/25774491/detail.html\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>The folks in Dickson County are still waiting for their $1 million in flood assistance from the federal government. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/25772239/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>The Nashville Zoo is offering free admission for active duty military, veterans and their immediate families on Sunday for Military Appreciation Day. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20101112/NEWS01/101112020/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li><li>David Kernall was sentenced to serve one year in a halfway house for hacking into Sarah Palin&#x2019;s personal Yahoo account. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=13491638\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li></ul><p><em>Photo by </em><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/denisemattox/5169966491/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><em>niseag03</em></a><em>.</em></p><p>No related posts.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}